---
title: Pasanda Spiced Chicken Curry with Cumin Rice and Courgette
description: Pasanda curries are fragrant and gently spiced Indian dishes that are usually rich and creamy. Here, we've got chicken and fried courgette, perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour of the pasanda curry sauce.
